fr:mainmatter.fr:p:
Let C be a well-powered category with
pullbacks. Then the (contravariant) subobject functor
C^\text {op}\xrightarrow {\operatorname {Sub}_C} Set acts on subobjects by
pullback: 




    \usepackage{tikz, tikz-cd, mathtools, amssymb}
